# Shorten /kitchens/home/… to /… — the home kitchen has a friendly root
# alias, and every in-app link canonically builds /kitchens/${kitchen}/…
# shapes. These rules flip the long form back to the short alias at the
# Cloudflare Pages edge for external / bookmark / typed-URL traffic.
# In-app <Link> clicks are handled client-side by a parallel React Router
# redirect route. 301 because Cloudflare _redirects doesn't support 308;
# 301 is close enough for the GET traffic we serve here.
/kitchens/home        /         301
/kitchens/home/*      /:splat   301
